data.enText: a type of food made from grains of maize ( corn ) that are heated until they burst, forming light whitish balls that are then covered with salt or sugar

simple_means.memory_skill: pop n.流行音乐 + corn n.谷物

tr: small kernels of corn exploded by heat
corn having small ears and kernels that burst when exposed to dry heat

value.def: Popcorn is a snack which consists of grains of maize or corn that have been heated until they have burst and become large and light. It can be eaten with salt or sometimes sugar.

trans: 鸡米花；雞米花；劲爆鸡米花；炸鸡；米花
